data.description: Discover the charm of this home, bathed in natural light throughout its welcoming interior. The eat-in kitchen is perfect for gathering and entertaining. The owners suite bedroom offers ample space and tranquility, complemented by a bathroom featuring split double vanities and a garden tub. Nestled on a generous corner lot with a side-entry garage and abundant parking This inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home features a well-designed split floor plan, showcasing new carpeting in the bedrooms and fresh interior paint throughout. The backyard, generously sized and enclosed with a fence, offers versatility and includes a convenient shed - pre-wired for electricity. Noteworthy updates include a roof replacement in 2014 and new siding installed in 2019. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
